headline: Freedom Capital Upgrades Abbott Laboratories (ABT) to Buy
summary: ​Abbott Laboratories (NYSE:ABT) is one of the Best 52-Week Low Stocks to Invest In. On January 29, Freedom Capital upgraded the stock from Hold to Buy, but lowered the price target from $130 to $120.
